-!- FUNCTION: Involved in export of lead, cadmium, zinc and mercury.
-!- CATALYTIC ACTIVITY: ATP + H(2)O + Cd(2+)(In) = ADP + phosphate +
    Cd(2+)(Out).
-!- CATALYTIC ACTIVITY: ATP + H(2)O + Zn(2+)(In) = ADP + phosphate +
    Zn(2+)(Out).
-!- SUBCELLULAR LOCATION: Cell inner membrane; multi-pass membrane
    protein.
-!- SIMILARITY: Belongs to the cation transport ATPase (P-type)
    family. Type IB subfamily.
-!- SIMILARITY: Contains 1 HMA domain.
